frames.caption: Three riders on horseback gallop along a beach under a stunning starry sky. The scene is illuminated by the glow of the Milky Way, creating a magical and adventurous atmosphere. The ocean waves gently lap at the horses' hooves as they move forward.
frames.description: The image captures a serene yet dynamic scene of horseback riding on a beach at night. The riders are silhouetted against a breathtaking celestial backdrop, with the Milky Way prominently visible. The ocean and sky blend seamlessly, creating a sense of wonder and exploration.

The horses create splashes as they move through the shallow water, with the ocean stretching out to the horizon. The scene is illuminated by the soft glow of the celestial display above.
